title: Gratitude and Celebration
description:
Sadie kicks off Season 2 by welcoming Pastor Rich & DawnChere Wilkerson Jr. to the podcast. They discuss how to stay focused in the chaos of life, the importance of gratitude and celebration, and of course, share the best piece of advice they have ever received! Pastor Rich & DawnChere Wilkerson Jr. planted and pastor VOUS Church in Miami. vouschurch.com
